      "para_id": "Q004397.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) Šu-Suen , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters : Kug-Ningal , child of Kalaĝu , the temple administrator of Ninsumun , is your servant ."
    }
